<br>
Granted this may be lvl 50 plus only but here goes. <br>
<br>
Useing the MSII pets per big fight or just as extra dmg in measureable allotments.  <br>
<br>
Example fight in BW:  summon pet ms2,  send on wurm, debuff wurm, a choice nuke, dmg shield tanks, mana at 70.  when wurm hits fear mode reclaim pet let party finish.  result 80 to 90 mana depending on dmg shield casts, often before next pull (kinda slow) can have a new pet summoned and be at 90 mana.<br>
<br>
Now for the faster pull/kills you leave pet out of fight untill you get one or two nukes off which insure your percentage dmg over rules what pet will do send pet. If mana is low reclaim pet before end of fight and depending on how low mana gets make and reclaim several pets.  takes me about 5-6 pets to get a full blue bub of mana.  if you do this while pulls are comming in each pet can add dmg thus insureing your contribution to the fight. <br>
<br>
In constantly rotating pets via reclaim you basically keep a pet up for most of the fight times which is as usefull as keeping one pet up all the time anyway.  The added benifit is that you get a mana boost for every pet you reclaim.  (if you didnt know already, you get a little more mana back for reclaiming the high hit point pets earth or ms2 are the winners) so its like makeing intrest on your mana investment.<br>
<br>
You get the benifits of pet dmg and a little mana back.  My best example of how powerfull this can be is when i was hunting vampires and we had and over pull.  The enchanter was keeping controll but runing out of mana very fast. <br>
i rodded untill i was at 20 mana and then started cycling pets and every 4th or 5th pet I was able to rod chanter.  it was a very successfull long fight.   <br>
<br>
so between the two mod rod spells and a pet i can boost my mana up to 8 bars in theroy and then given malacite and time i can build mana or cycle pets to cast essintial spells. i keep 2 mod rods on all party members that are willing to hold them.  It really banks a LOT of mana!.<br>
<br>
some factors for me, i specialize in conjuration, my int is about 220 take or give (buffs/gear).  I sit on a cheap horse every chance i get cause its a standing meditate mode (the biggest reason ever to get a horse for me) im 56 and have mod rod 1 and 2.<br>
